{"tid":1323211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家開始嘅喺香港保衛戰，拒絕香港送終","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:54.000Z","uid":52609,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4b608b23202679c7976ffc08d0e4c45dfb66af97","tid":1323211,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完你老母</span></strong></span><br />\n而家開始嘅喺<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港保衛戰</span></span></strong>，拒絕香港送終<br />\n<br />\n港共殺人政權點會容許成立獨立調查委員會調查自己嘅武裝力量<br />\n港共殺人政權點會容許放義士，比我地繼續抗爭<br />\n只有普選先可以選擇代表香港人嘅政府<br />\n只有普選先可以保住香港<br />\n只有普選先可以保住我地嘅自由<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這是一場香港保衛戰</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求當中其實有啲已經無用，有需要再次更改次序<br />\n<br />\n一： 全面撤回《引渡條例》<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n二： 成立獨立調查委員會調查警察濫權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三： 釋放被捕人士並承諾不檢控任何示威者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四： 撤銷暴動定性<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五： 立即在八三一框架外實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新次序應該喺<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一： 立即在八三一框架外實行雙普選<br />\n二： 成立獨立調查委員會調查警察濫權<br />\n三： 釋放被捕人士並承諾不檢控任何示威者<br />\n四： 撤銷暴動定性<br />\n五： 全面撤回《引渡條例》</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"af02ae6e219f9a58e6479ba212821531edddb03d","tid":1323211,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"cb65da814b15ed7465f0decfc1d49d9ad5405ef0","tid":1323211,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2f50bfb66f6a6e710f18a5d89a93513c0e3661d","tid":1323211,"uid":209689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"囗號要叫香港保衛戰！"},{"pid":"6c56c87d8ac301a9b0bd32d8c197edd2cd2dbe44","tid":1323211,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"奪回香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da890e0f6308d58c23e36b21672f8d312959ae34","tid":1323211,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"拎返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678116dba636af0b08a8c07c07049d4ecbd5391e","tid":1323211,"uid":111269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d780aa669777aa3e5a683bc91415cd9becb84f1d","tid":1323211,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a99d23c05db1a3b8ce2922a133efeaa2af30198","tid":1323211,"uid":252854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"推 還我香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0fe9da83aac4171ce9024af89155c5eb90bee5","tid":1323211,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ee99c84712a8bc5b15985678d644d52f